{"tid":1613274,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐聯前瞻：美斯做巴塞救世主 盧卡古缺陣國米","createTime":"2019-10-02T13:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T10:56:50.000Z","uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63f73b3c7f834e0df68b09554d07ccc4e7bdcb75","tid":1613274,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"歐聯前瞻：美斯做巴塞救世主 盧卡古缺陣國米<br />\n<br />\n自上屆歐聯被利物浦大逆轉、最後恥辱性出局的巴塞，之後就交上噩運，西班牙盃決賽不敵華倫西亞，美斯更於美洲國家盃受傷，到現在亦未傷化。雖然今夏重心購入基沙文，荷蘭新貴法蘭基迪莊亦來投，但球隊缺少美斯下進退失據，於西甲演出令人失望。首場歐聯分組賽僅能作客打和多蒙特0:0，今次主場出擊必求3分。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯現時仍然有傷，但名字出現在大軍名單當中，就算不正選登場也會列於後備席。奧士文尼迪比利亦已復操，但狀態未出難當正選，預料領隊華維迪將用基沙文及蘇亞雷斯掛帥，新星安素法迪則因傷缺陣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國米於干地領導下，本季演出大躍進，於意甲取得6連勝，壓倒祖雲達斯領導群雄。但前曼聯射手盧卡古卻未能出場，將大大減低攻力。上仗聯賽鬥森多利亞，A山神正選出場兼有士哥，今仗倒戈勢爭表現。<br />\n<br />\n不過山齊士狀態反覆 難有穩定表現 今仗作客真係輸硬都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f186d5256b095d795c80158e76b9b118131c35","tid":1613274,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"美斯今鋪發威了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5784c3ac33dadaa28bdde2587445c102e15905b","tid":1613274,"uid":204306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b6f186d5256b095d795c80158e76b9b118131c35","tid":1613274,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"美斯今鋪發威了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:19:01.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"54ed010b897dfb3f8d77df4f5205018efedfa47a","tid":1613274,"uid":279463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6f186d5256b095d795c80158e76b9b118131c35","tid":1613274,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"美斯今鋪發威了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/02/222456_8a61cfa6f6a0322866c72b637e97c9d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2F222456_8a61cfa6f6a0322866c72b637e97c9d9.png&h=ded7619f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5409cbca4555bb55e95837a52ade49760e6d6c01","tid":1613274,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:49:41.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"9c1a52464b02338c0c4d57e75e1230b3c5a24b8a","tid":1613274,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5409cbca4555bb55e95837a52ade49760e6d6c01","tid":1613274,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:49:41.000Z","msg":"中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"係"}]}